title: FSX - FTX - Orbx - Australia Red
description:
Here's the final region for Australia released by the wonderful people over at FTX- the Red Zone, including the wonderful Ayers Rock area.  It looks like fantastic scenery, so you'll definitely want to check it out.  

It's the original installer- no rip here, so just install and you're good to go.

I don't take credit for this- only for uploading it here on TPB.  Credit goes to those wonderful folks over at FSWC.  

Now if we could only get FsP X, then life would be complete....  haha.  Okay, maybe that and the FS DreamTeam stuff...  

Anyway- enjoy the scenery....
